{"tid":1119310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【快點 ...】指導未成年男學生變發生關係　女教練被控誘拐兒童罪","createTime":"2019-04-21T22:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T00:12:04.000Z","uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a8a30238701a2fa011694078cf9e4c2cae25f56","tid":1119310,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:05:20.000Z","msg":"指導未成年男學生變發生關係 女教練被控誘拐兒童罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190422/photo/bkn-20190422030054299-0422_00972_001_01p.jpg?20190422031018\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190422%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190422030054299-0422_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20190422031018&h=7045988c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國印第安納州韋恩堡一名高中女體育教練，前年與一名未成年的男學生交換聯絡方法，希望藉此指導對方，詎料雙方其後發生關係。女體育教練更一度哀求男學生的母親，希望這段不倫的師生關係能夠持續下去。她最終被控兩項誘拐兒童罪，將於周二（23日）出庭應訊。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，26歲的普西（Cayla Pusey）曾為一間高中擔任體育教練，前年4月與一名男學生交換聯絡方法。雙方其後互傳裸照和情慾短訊，最終發展成性關係。男學生供稱，自己曾經到過普西的家約5至10次。<br />\n<br />\n普西曾經聯絡男學生的母親，希望對方容許兩人繼續交往，不過遭到拒絕。男學生的母親其後要求兩人結束關係，並承諾只要普西願意離開就不會報警。"},{"pid":"022ab3edb90dc17947f69d3cd1b1198836833c59","tid":1119310,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:05:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190422/mobile/bkn-20190422030054299-0422_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190422%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190422030054299-0422_00972_001.html&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=a8f59f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190422/mobile/bkn-20190422030054299-0422_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b59cd41800159cd6f509704bf820363c677b6cb6","tid":1119310,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:06:09.000Z","msg":"Pussy 教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52f1a85c8498fa3004ff3fcd6cbe9e5eceb8167